Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is a tomb\Ndeep in the forbidden land.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A burial ground for gift-users,\Nreferred to as the Grave.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is here that vengeful spirits\Nof the supernaturally gifted{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}transform into Grotesqueries.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To prevent their escape,\Nthey are sealed away.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As supernatural abilities are linked\Nto spiritual power,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if the Grotesqueries were ever awakened,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it would mean an unprecedented crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,for everyone in the imperial capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The real question we face is\Nwho would unseal the Grave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and for what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The revelation\Nthat came to His Highness Takaihito,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't have been a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He isn't certain.\NHe says that his powers aren't steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Once he ascends to the throne,\Nhe should fully inherit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Try as we might,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we could never comprehend this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,as he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen you two for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kudo and Mr. Okaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuishi, your outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you intend to appear\Nbefore His Highness in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.21,0:01:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Military officers have a uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And since I'm not one,\Nthe only rules I should follow are orders
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,direct from the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't there be\Na minimum level of etiquette?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you see is my formal wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to be\Nsuch a stiff about clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I will let this slide, but only once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to get all wound up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have arrived, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okaito, Kudo, and lastly, Tatsuishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You may enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,MY HAPPY MARRIAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 8\NNIGHTMARES AND OMINOUS SHADOWS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been far too long,\NYour Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Far too long, indeed,\NI am glad to see you all well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, I wish to introduce myself\Nas the new head of the Tatsuishis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kazushi Tatsuishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful\Nthat you would grant me an audience today
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,despite the recent disgrace\Nupon my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He committed a crime most severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly hope it had caused little trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You need not fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine\Nit was easy for you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sire, your words are far too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We will begin anew\Nwith guidance from the Kudos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,With their family's guiding hand\Nand watchful eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do my best, my utmost
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to restore honor and trust\Nfollowing their command.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,On behalf of my father, the Emperor,\NI forgive the Tatsuishi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Strive to live up to the words\Nyou have spoken in earnest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I am grateful for your generosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now then, the revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was told\Nyou've had one recently, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I have little doubt that you are now\Naware of the Grave being unsealed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From the realm of the dead,\Na never-ending night will come.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is a deep and eternal darkness\Nwith no end.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be careful. There will be a battle.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If things go poorly,\Nsome may lose their lives.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So the danger is already here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's approaching the imperial capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I will immediately inform you\Nif I see anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We will now take our leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiyoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you got engaged
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- at long last.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fiancée is certainly interesting.\NAlthough, things are going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a little bit difficult\Nfor you before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry yourself.\NI've no doubt you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a revelation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I will stay mindful of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh! Mm-hm.\N- Uh, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,First things first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll want to keep your back\Nas stick straight as you possibly can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right.\N- Eyes stay forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right.\N- Parties are meant for socializing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have much experience\Nin that area, so we'll focus there first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay.\N- Now, give us a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Try lifting the corners of your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Oh, here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A while ago, I took Kiyoka out\Nto this little sweets shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So of course we ordered some.\NYou basically have to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But what was he interested in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly wasn't the sweets,\Nso what do you think it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They served us pickles\Nas a side for the sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved them so much that he asked
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,if he could start having\Npickles for dessert
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He acts so stoic, but he loves to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he really say that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get that smile\Nto be your natural one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I like to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up,\Nyou'll practice walking in a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Movement in a dress\Nis different than a kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,ONE: ETIQUETTE FOR WESTERN ATTIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,TWO: SMILE WHEN GREETING
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,THREE: TABLE MANNERS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's phenomenal.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miss Hazuki is a real proper lady.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In our lessons, I get to learn\Na bit more from her every day.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}It feels like... I'm slowly coming\Nto know her better.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}It's like a ray of sunshine\Ngetting closer to me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I can become a proper lady,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}one who's suitable\Nof being with Lord Kudo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His Highness knows something...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or at least has some idea\Nof what's about to happen to Miyo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure how to help her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's about Shinichi's first wife.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're truly not gonna believe it\Nwhen I tell you about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman was a blood relative\Nof the Usuba family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Usuba family.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Among all households\Nwith supernatural gifts,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they are considered exceptional\Nand often seen as a threat.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They possess the ability to read minds,\Nlook into one's memories,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and even enter another's dream\Nwhile they sleep.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are Miyo's nightmares...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}linked to someone in the Usuba family?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The barrier around the house is unbroken,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and there are no signs\Nof external intruders.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ruling those out,\Nthe only possibility left is...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We could move at any moment.\NGet what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you heading out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am. Won't take me long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, is our Commander\Ngoing off to see Miss Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for work. I will return before dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Do as you will, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll want to cover\Nhow to introduce yourself to others,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the intricacies of conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and how to handle any of the troublemakers\Nshould they try to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so grateful for you.\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all\Nfor my kind, sweet little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can help you succeed in any way,\Nthen I'm more than happy to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a small favor, really,\Nand you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like we've gotten close enough\Nthat I can ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but is it still a strange request?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Hazuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uh, it's just about how you address me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to lose the "Miss".\NIt feels too formal, wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'd like if the two of us could work on\Ngetting to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You are joining the family after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I want you to feel safe\Nin relying on me for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Kiyoka feels the same way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,even though he doesn't show it very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rely on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're one of us now.\NFormalities aren't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you would call me "sister",\NI would be more than okay with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Of course,\NI want that to be a choice you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear sister.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,May I just call you "Hazuki" instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, Miyo.\NSee you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Thank you for your time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want very much\Nto be by Lord Kudo's side.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want very much to become\Na family with him someday.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...what does it mean being "family"?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fun,\Nstarted raining out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can never tell\Nwhat summer weather has in store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Did you find them?\NThe Usubas are difficult to track down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've looked into em'\Nevery way I could imagine to,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but there isn't a single record\Nor document with that family's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Best I found were some rumors\Nin circulation that mention 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So there's one lead,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the single thread to the Usuba family\Nis Sumi Usuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She was the only one\Nwho used the last name,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}which makes her the only Usuba we know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We know that Sumi Usuba existed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She married into the Saimoris\Nand had Miyo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They can try to keep this a secret,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but completely erasing\Nher entire existence would be impossible.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get whatever information you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name was Sumi,\Nso search any records with that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Comb the imperial capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will figure this out.\NShe's suffering with these nightmares.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How did that one look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that was\Nthe best you've done so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have done it without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,With how far you've come,\NI'd say it's time to go into town
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and give everything a real test run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Miyo, are you okay? Is this too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been sleeping enough at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- I am.\N- Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me if this gets too stressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If I heard correctly,\NKiyoka's been coming home later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He said his workload was increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, he'll likely\Nbe staying there again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he ever choose work\Nover his sweet, adorable fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bad sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he's at work\Nbusy giving it his best,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to do the same here\Nworking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you, huh! And what a smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Commander, there's an envoy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}from the Ministry\Nof the Imperial Household.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They finally decided to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird, right?\NThey're usually so secretive over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and this time,\Nthey're right on our doorstep?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, it communicates\Nhow urgent the situation is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious as to what they'll say,\Nso we'll let them take the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Arata Tsuruki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,SPECIAL ADVISOR ARATA TSURUKI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Messenger for the Ministry\Nof the Imperial House.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kiyoka Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander of\Nthe Special Anti-Grotesquerie Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In several circles of society,\Nyou're quite famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The ladies speak ill of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Unapproachable, and cold\Nas a frozen tundra", so I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no need of such intel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I only require information on the Grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know by now,\Nthe Grave has been unsealed recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ministry is in a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They're currently racing\Nto retrieve the Grotesqueries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And the motive for unsealing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's still under investigation,\Nbut what they did find
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,were a multitude of suspicious men\Ncollapsed near the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be natural to assume\Nthat they're the ones who did this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but their purpose is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the Ministry deciding to share
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,all of these classified details\Nwith us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're usually more hesitant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, only 20 percent\Nof the Grotesqueries have been retrieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There are also victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Clearly, they are\Ntoo short-staffed to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher-ups of the Ministry needed\Nsome convincing to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Does something trouble you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is rude, I apologize,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but what circumstances led you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not Ministry staff, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What a keen eye you have, Mr. Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not employed\Nby the Ministry of the Imperial Household.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I've had a relationship\Nwith them for a long while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Most often, one would find me\Nrunning a company called Tsuruki Trading.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm usually quite immersed\Nresearching and doing negotiations
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,with our various business partners,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but if they ask, I'll take on\Njobs like this every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. A negotiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When they have a situation\Nthat's more than they can handle,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,they call you in, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which,\Nbefore the negotiations,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I also did a little research on you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as I knew\Nwe were going to be meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and congratulations\Non your recent engagement, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a lie to say\Nthat I wasn't envious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that we all would like to find\Na companion we enjoy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,with the eventual prospect\Nof settling down with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is no easy task.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the whole concept of marriage\Nis difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As this is a formal request,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we are happy to offer assistance\Nwith whatever the Ministry needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And we thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I will very likely be\Nyour point of contact
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,for any further operations from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward\Nto working alongside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And likewise. Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you the best of luck, Mr. Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Worse than I could've imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as you see\Na Grotesquerie, you will report in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you encounter one,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,be sure that others are with you\Nto deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He was found collapsed\Nin the bushes nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I do detect a faint pulse,\Nbut he's out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So this one is the same\Nas the others mentioned in the report?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor guy! But I guess\N"victim" isn't the only title he's got.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. From what we can tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,he's one of the perpetrators\Nin the unsealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So when he wakes up,\Nhe's got a scary interrogation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for him\Nwhenever he's cognizant again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Guy can't catch a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's {\i1}if{\i} he comes to again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.77,0:16:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Several other men in this state\Nwere discovered back at the Grave site,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but none are awake yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can figure out\Nwhy they're like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're weak,\Nbut none of them should be catatonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And we're assuming it's a curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We suspect that they came into contact\Nwith a Grotesquerie
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that had recently been freed\Nfrom the Grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you understand,\N{\i1}kaijutsu's{\i} the type of work I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,While it does allow me\Nto undo a curse or technique,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it would only work on the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lifting a curse on the dead\Nis a whole other skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no alternative.\NDo your best, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,From the looks of things,\Nsomething was taken out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander? Do you sense something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound... just vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This curse is really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}More than I can handle. It's overwhelming...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's that?\N- Keep your distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Though they were once one of us,\Nthe moment they turn into
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,vengeful Grotesqueries\Nthat attack the living...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we must take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:19:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one way.\NI cannot allow you to roam freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... the signs are already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The awakening will be soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And I, its protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.11,0:19:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}After all, it is my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They're awful. Grave Grotesqueries...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If we had to face an army of these\Nat the imperial capital...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We won't let that happen...\Nno matter what.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, sir. Can I get one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely! I think you're doing very well!\NYour hard work shows!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your walk, down to your posture, is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to your instruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,While this is still a lesson,\Nit's important to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's practical training day.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Kudo is working so hard\Nwith all those long days,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so I have to work hard too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to become a proper lady\Nthat's suitable for him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking awfully pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, I feel fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a break is part of working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't rush learning all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already doing\Neverything you need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no need to overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, why don't we go home for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Hazuki, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to go home\Nand get some proper rest. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.41,0:21:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for your own good.\NThere's no need to rush this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't want to prepare for an event,\Nonly to get sick. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!\NStorytime is starting, so listen close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hurry up! Hurry up!
